        "\n",
        "### 6.1 Fitting the Best ARIMA Model\n",
        "\n",
        "We now fit the optimal ARIMA(p, d, q) model identified by the grid search on the **full training set** (80% of the data). The remaining 20% is held out as the **test set** to evaluate out-of-sample forecast performance.\n",
        "\n",
